{"tid":593354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田家庭糾紛有人搶去警員配槍後開槍　一警中槍受傷","createTime":"2018-03-15T02:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T03:03:17.000Z","uid":4493,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15eb4ea13f4ac069d33d7908681f3f78c2810419","tid":593354,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=257398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D257398&d=IJsfNq5cxxdb7iavmc3bl%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d1c57865\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D257398&h=ad2cf481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=257398</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/102309_81bdac8311cafbb71044fd5bf62ca96e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F102309_81bdac8311cafbb71044fd5bf62ca96e.png&h=93d5f672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】沙田廣林苑清晨發生搶槍及開槍案，三人受傷送院包括兩名警員。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑搶槍及開槍的疑犯黑布蒙頭送往威爾斯醫院，其餘兩名傷者是警員，其中一名警員中槍，另一名警員擦傷，送院時清醒。<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰早上前往醫院了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n現場是沙田小瀝源廣林苑茂林閣一個單位。清晨約五時三十分，警方接獲一宗家庭糾紛案，其間有人醉酒情緒激動，一度與警員對峙，搶去警員配槍後開槍，警方正在現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bc9c88aca3b95ff8f7426d586e4f6602024dd1","tid":593354,"uid":37989,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:27:31.000Z","msg":"兩名傷者都係警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d9f9e87e881a7e3ce9213f39cd21e11aa192a9","tid":593354,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit